# Final Outcome

By the end of the implementation phase, the platform will support:

* Restaurant discovery using geospatial queries
* Food ordering and checkout system
* Real-time order tracking
* Dine-out reservations
* Gamified review system
* Merchant and courier dashboards
* Cloud deployment

This architecture ensures the platform is **scalable, modular, and production-ready**.
